data.description: Welcome home to 688 Whippoorwill Lane! Original owners of this 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath colonial on a cul-de-sac. 1st Floor features 9' ceilings, 1st floor laundry, cherry kitchen with stainless steel appliances opens to the Great Room and formal dining room. Attached 2 car garage. Upstairs you will find a large Master Suite with walk-in closet, mater bath with garden tub and stand alone shower and double sinks. 2 More ample size bedrooms and a full bath. Deck with private backyard. All new carpet on the 2nd floor in Sept. 2023. Dishwasher only 4 months old. New HWT Oct. 2023. Full unfinished basement waiting for you to finish or use as storage. Pre-approved buyers only please!
